  "markup": "\u003Carticle id=\u0022page-copy\u0022 class=\u0022article-content\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cp\u003EBe sure to also check out our \u003Ca href=\u0022/faqs\u0022\u003EFAQs page\u003C/a\u003E for a list of our most commonly asked questions. Still don\u0026rsquo;t find the answer you need? Then contact us at:\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003ELaser Therapy U LLC\u003Cbr /\u003E\n201 E. Ohio St. #2720\u003Cbr /\u003E\nChicago, IL 60611\u003Cbr /\u003E\nEmail: \u003Ca href=\u0022mailto:info@lasertherapyu.org?subject=LTU.org%20Site%20Inquiry\u0022\u003Einfo@lasertherapyu.org\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr /\u003E\nPhone: 1-678-233-1425\u003Cbr /\u003E\nFax: 1-866-314-6706\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks,\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Laser Therapy U Team\u003C/p\u003E\n    \u003C/article\u003E\n\n    \u003Carticle id=\u0022confirmation\u0022 class=\u0022article-content\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cp\u003EThank you.\u003C/p\u003E\n    \u003C/article\u003E\n\n\u003Ca href=\u0022tel:1-440-715-5075\u0022\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022contact-info\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022contact-info-content\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022contact-info-shell\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Ch3 class=\u0022contact-info-h3\u0022\u003E\n                    If you need further information about Laser Therapy University or laser therapy products, please call:\n                \u003C/h3\u003E\n                \u003Ch2 class=\u0022contact-info-h2\u0022\u003E1-678-233-1425\u003C!--\u003Ca id=\u0022content_0_controls_0_hlPhoneNumber\u0022 title=\u0022678-233-1425\u0022 href=\u0022tel:\u002B6782331425\u0022\u003E678-233-1425\u003C/a\u003E--\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/a\u003E\n\n    \u003Csection id=\u0022form-container\u0022 class=\u0022content-form\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cul class=\u0022form form-column form-column-1\u0022\u003E\n\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Cinput type=\u0022hidden\u0022 name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$LeadSource\u0022 id=\u0022LeadSource\u0022 value=\u0022Website: LTU Contact Us\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    First Name*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbFirstName\u0022 type=\u0022text\u0022 id=\u0022tbFirstName\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input  isrequired\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    Last Name*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbLastName\u0022 type=\u0022text\u0022 id=\u0022tbLastName\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input  isrequired\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    Email Address*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbEmailAddress\u0022 type=\u0022email\u0022 id=\u0022tbEmailAddress\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input  isrequired\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    Company Name / Practice Name\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbCompanyName\u0022 type=\u0022text\u0022 id=\u0022tbCompanyName\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    Address*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbAddress\u0022 type=\u0022text\u0022 id=\u0022tbAddress\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input isrequired\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    City*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Cinput name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$tbCity\u0022 type=\u0022text\u0022 id=\u0022tbCity\u0022 class=\u0022form-text-input  isrequired\u0022 /\u003E\n            \u003C/li\u003E\n            \u003Cli class=\u0022form-item\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Clabel class=\u0022form-label\u0022\u003E\n                    Country*\u003C/label\u003E\n                \u003Ca class=\u0022selectFix\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cspan class=\u0022dropdown-label\u0022\u003E\n                        Select Country\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan class=\u0022dropArrow\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Cimg src=\u0022/presentation/laseru/images/dropArrowDark.png\u0022 /\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n                    \u003Cselect name=\u0022content_0$controls_0$ddlCountry\u0022 id=\u0022ddlCountry\u0022 class=\u0022form-selectbox  isrequired\u0022\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022\u0022\u003ESelect Country\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022United States\u0022\u003EUnited States\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Afghanistan\u0022\u003EAfghanistan\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022\u0413\u2026land Islands\u0022\u003E\u0026#197;land Islands\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Albania\u0022\u003EAlbania\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Algeria\u0022\u003EAlgeria\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022American Samoa\u0022\u003EAmerican Samoa\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Andorra\u0022\u003EAndorra\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Angola\u0022\u003EAngola\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u003Coption value=\u0022Anguilla\u0022\u003EAnguilla\u003C/option\u003E\n\t\u0